      <t>This document describes a deadline based deterministic forwarding mechanism for IP/MPLS network with the corresponding resource reservation, admission control, scheduling and policing processes to provide guaranteed latency bound. It employs a latency compensation technique with a stateless core, to replace reshaping, making it suitable for the Differentiated Services (Diffserv) architecture [RFC2475].</t>
